data.name: TextGraphicObject
desc: specifies a graphic which can be embedded in Text.

properties.name: ActualSize
desc: contains the original size of the bitmap in the graphic object.

properties.name: AdjustBlue
desc: changes the display of the blue color channel.
It contains percentage values between -100 and +100.

properties.name: AdjustContrast
desc: changes the display of contrast.
It contains percentage values between -100 and +100.

properties.name: AdjustGreen
desc: changes the display of the green color channel.
It contains percentage values between -100 and +100.

properties.name: AdjustLuminance
desc: changes the display of the luminance.
It contains percentage values between -100 and +100.

properties.name: AdjustRed
desc: changes the display of the red color channel.
It contains percentage values between -100 and +100.

properties.name: ContentProtected
desc: determines if the content is protected against changes from the user interface.

properties.name: ContourOutside
desc: the text flows only around the contour of the object.

properties.name: ContourPolyPolygon
desc: contains the contour of the object as PolyPolygon.

properties.name: Gamma
desc: determines the gamma value of the graphic.

properties.name: Graphic
desc: contains the background graphic of the object.

properties.name: GraphicColorMode
desc: contains the ColorMode as com.sun.star.drawing.ColorMode.

properties.name: GraphicCrop
desc: contains the cropping of the object.

properties.name: GraphicFilter
desc: contains the name of the filter of the background graphic of the object.

properties.name: GraphicIsInverted
desc: determines if the graphic is display in inverted colors.
It contains percentage values between -100 and +100.

properties.name: GraphicURL
desc: contains the URL of the background graphic of the object

Note the new behaviour since it was deprecated: This property can only be set and only external URLs are supported (no more vnd.sun.star.GraphicObject scheme). When a URL is set, then it will load the image and set the Graphic property.

properties.name: HoriMirroredOnEvenPages
desc: determines if the object is horizontally mirrored on even pages.

properties.name: HoriMirroredOnOddPages
desc: determines if the object is horizontally mirrored on odd pages.

properties.name: ImageMap
desc: returns the client-side image map if one is assigned to the object.

properties.name: SurroundContour
desc: determines if the text wraps around the contour of the object.

properties.name: Transparency
desc: contains percentage values between -100 and +100.

properties.name: VertMirrored
desc: determines if the object is mirrored vertically.
